VEGGIE PIZZA

Ingredients:
- Pizza dough
- Pizza sauce
- Fresh cherry tomatoes, bell peppers, spinach, artichoke hearts (or similar veggies)
- Mozzarella cheese

Instructions:
1. Preheat the oven to around 450°F (230°C).
2. Roll or stretch the dough, then spread a thin layer of pizza sauce.
3. Top with a colorful array of cherry tomatoes, sliced bell peppers, spinach, artichokes, or other favorite veggies.
4. Cover evenly with shredded mozzarella.
5. Bake until the crust is golden and cheese is bubbly (typically around 20 minutes).
